=== Start a DVCS repository ===

for Mercurial,
    >>> hg init; rm .gitignore; hg commit -A

for Git,
    >>> git init; rm .hgignore; git commit -a

=== Building and running ===

To build this project, use
    >>> mvn compile exec:java -Dexec.mainClass=${package}.MyAppMain -Dexec.args="-h"

Take out the "-h" and replace it with whatever arguments your project might require.
